import React, { Component } from 'react' export default class About extends Component { render() { return (
About Me

Who Am I?

I am a software engineer and scrum master from Falcon, Colorado.I love exploring new technologies and am often amazed by the progress we as a human species have made so far.

I have started playing around with react again lately and decided to build this site.

What I do?

Here are some things I have experience with

Web Development

I have experience building websites using JavaScript,React,HTML,CSS

Radar Systems

In my current position I am working on the next generation radar

Dev Ops

I work with tools like Jenkins, Fisheye, Crucible

Agile

In my current position I am a scrum master and use tools like Jira

Graphic Design

I offer Logo and website design

Project Management

I have led many Software teams through all development stages.

) } }
